{"tid":1632064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位我地係時候還原基本步：雙十死線","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:18:53.000Z","uid":67340,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8471d3d6e15123e5a2a6a1fa091843fab3d7f59e","tid":1632064,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"TLDR:<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雙十死線<br />\n雙十死線<br />\n雙十死線</span></span><br />\n<br />\n辛苦各位手足和理非嘅行動同討論<br />\n榮光盡歸英雄 盡歸香港<br />\n<br />\n講翻正題<br />\n唔少聲音擔心勇武過火，唔少勇武亦相信行動嘅重要<br />\n加上晚晚行動，前線折損速度絕對比以前一周幾次嘅行動快，而反蒙面法現實上令我地處境更凶險<br />\n<br />\n文宣係需要時間煲嘅<br />\n如果係咁，我地就還原基本步<br />\n設<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雙十死線</span></span><br />\n死線前<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">答應五大訴求，並立即取消禁蒙面法</span></span><br />\n否則繼續裝修，繼續抗命<br />\n<br />\n無論和勇，我地嘅民意同決心都係澄明嘅<br />\n所以呢幾日要全力谷大國際戰線，為雙十死線加大壓力<br />\n我地已經轉入直路，只要有技巧地踩實油門，少失誤，勝利女神露埋對波仔俾你玩都得<br />\n<br />\n天琦，我仍記得你信中嘅一字一句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保持思考<br />\n</span></span><br />\n香港人，煲底還是地獄谷底，我們一齊走到尾，好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雙十死線<br />\n雙十死線<br />\n雙十死線</span></span>"},{"pid":"c338b3b19612f017011d07e36f134bdca0cb8cc8","tid":1632064,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:49.000Z","msg":"推到各方英雄入黎"},{"pid":"df08a75c06575f47feb35833d41b724b004ae600","tid":1632064,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:15.000Z","msg":"推到民記入黎"},{"pid":"a094e8fc83b6b6fb6a7d471fef23675840931fa0","tid":1632064,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:29.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"7343235c5577e8751f1a41c1dc3ecee346d59d29","tid":1632064,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:44.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"6225b5418fa7727257f0395a32d33508819b4abc","tid":1632064,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:55.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"32ae13f12ef1c878531fda85e8441b7ef2377c13","tid":1632064,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:07.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"93ced5aecfc359cf5beaf822da390e9c1396287a","tid":1632064,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:18.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"994c6f696bd74be437da1dc1f6971517bfecfde8","tid":1632064,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"d1d7f530d969d07e96904c2e03e64e3499f79aa7","tid":1632064,"uid":143401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />tui"},{"pid":"f62dc40a42cee2cd7f26ee906208b716da8cea1f","tid":1632064,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"5f950a0e0f381108addf662c7520e8ca4f861239","tid":1632064,"uid":67340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:40.000Z","msg":"求大家幫手推"},{"pid":"c5b5d447b51a9e47cd8e7506803532bb2d5dacaa","tid":1632064,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:40.000Z","msg":"10月10日真國慶日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家記得舉中華民國國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/